node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by CandyHunting on August 06, 2021 tagging @hyvee, @snickers, and @marswrigley. May be an image of food.

node.text:
Here are the new Snickers Almond Brownie & Dark Chocolate Squares! I found the stand up bags at Hy-Vee, and others have found the bars at stores including Walmart and Walgreens. 

This is the second Snickers Brownie candy bar, after the Peanut variety debuted last December. While the Peanut Brownie has a strong peanut flavor, the Almond Brownie has little almond flavor. There is some crunch from the almonds, but the flavor is dominated by the dark chocolate, chewy brownie filling, and caramel. I'm not a huge fan of almonds, so no almond flavor is a win for me. 

The Snickers Almond Brownie bars are pretty darn good! I would rank these slightly above the Peanut variety, but that is purely personal preference.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by CandyHunting on August 05, 2021 tagging @pepsico, and @mountaindew. May be an image of text that says 'new Voo MYSTERY FLAVOR 2021 DEK UNCOVER THE MYSTERY OF VOODEK'.

node.text:
Here is the new Mtn Dew Voo-Dew for 2021! This is the third edition of the mystery flavor, with the first two revealed to be Candy Corn and Fruity Candy Explosion. This third flavor strays far from the flavor of the first two. To me, it tastes like a cross between red licorice and cherry Starburst. It's seems like artificial cherry with something else going on, possibly tropical fruit? I've only tasted it at room temperature so far, as I just received the package. 

Huge, huge thanks to Mountain Dew for sending the new Voo-Dew! The package didn't list a release date, so I'm guessing it will hit shelves this month. Edit: The Dew should be out toward the end of August.

node.text: Famous Amos has a new Wonders of the World line set to hit shelves now! There are three varieties in the line: Belgian Chocolate Chip, Philippine Coconut & White Chocolate Chip, and Mediterranean Hazelnut & Chocolate Chip. Keep your eyes open for them, and I'll post as soon as I spot them in stores, as well. This picture was from the Sweets & Snacks Expo.

node.text:
New Pumpkin Spice Cup Noodles are hitting Walmart shelves at the end of October! The press release suggests topping the noodles with whipped cream for "the full pumpkin spice experience." 

Thoughts on this one? Yay or nay to pumpkin noodles?

node.text: New Crunchy Cookie M&M's are expected to debut in March 2022! They will be available in single, share, and stand up pouch size packs. Per the press release, these are intended to have the flavor profile of a chocolate chip cookie, although the images on the pack depict an M&M's cookie.

node.text: New Fusion Ice Cream Bars are out now at Aldi! The first flavor has vanilla ice cream and forest fruit sorbet coated in white chocolate and raspberry pieces. The second flavor has vanilla and caramel ice creams coated in milk chocolate with crunchy caramel pieces. Look for these in the Aldi Finds freezer!

node.text: Marble Slab Creamery has a new Flamin' Hot Cheetos ice cream and milkshake out now through September 30. The flavor has a sweet cream based mixed with Flamin' Hot Cheetos. I'm so disappointed that Marble Slab is mainly located in the south and has no locations in Wisconsin. /s
